sudoku.Seeds
public final class Seeds extends Object
Built-in Sudoku seed strings for quick loading in the CLI.

Each seed is an 81-character row-major string where digits 1..9 are givens and '0' or '.' represent empty cells.

Usage:


 String s = Seeds.BY_NAME.get("easy");
 Board b = Board.fromString(s);
